---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ZAI Institute"
  description="ZAI Institute is where universities launch AI programs, where enterprises train their workforce, and where senior operators think clearly about what AI is changing in their industry."
>
  <section class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-prose-wide">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-6">ZAI Institute</div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-h1 text-paper">
          Close the gap between what AI promises and what it delivers.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-body-lg text-paper/85 max-w-prose-narrow">
          AI is spreading through every organization. Almost no one can tell what is working, what is
          not, and what to do next. ZAI turns executive insight, university programs, and field
          research into measurable progress.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-display italic text-xl text-paper/70">
          The institution behind the institutions.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/for-universities" class="btn btn-primary">Launch an AI program</a>
          <a href="/for-organizations" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Train your workforce</a>
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Commission research</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-6">What we do</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink max-w-prose-wide">
        Programs that ship. Research that informs. A network that opens the room.
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-12 mt-12">
        <article>
          <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-3">01 &middot; Programs</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-3">
            Built on verified operator data, not theory.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
            University partners launch AI executive education programs under their own name in thirty
            days. No new hires. No accreditation review required. Faculty are trained, curriculum is
            built, and the first cohort fills before the next semester begins.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <a href="/for-universities" class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink">
              For universities &rsaquo;
            </a>
            <span class="mx-2 text-muted">/</span>
            <a href="/for-organizations" class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink">
              For organizations &rsaquo;
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article>
          <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-3">02 &middot; Research</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-3">
            Clear data on where AI investment produces results and where it stalls.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
            We interview senior operators about what they are actually building, what is working, and
            what is not. What we learn informs the published reports and the custom engagements that
            follow. It is built for the people making the decision, not for the briefing deck.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <a href="/research" class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink">
              Research engagements &rsaquo;
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article>
          <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-3">03 &middot; Network</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-3">
            Senior executives sharing what actually works.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
            The Advisory Board is eighteen named operators from across the Fortune 500. They sit at
            the center of a community of senior executives built across more than five hundred
            companies. Programs, research, and member access all flow through this circle.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <a href="/advisory-board" class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink">
              Advisory board &rsaquo;
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 border-t border-light-border pt-8">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-3">How ZAI works</div>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
          Programs create learning. Research creates proof. The network creates signal. Together they
          show what AI is changing and what to do next.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-ink-soft text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-6">By the numbers</div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10 mt-8">
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gold">60+</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-paper/80">Universities served, past decade</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gold">500+</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-paper/80">Companies represented</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-4xl md:text-5xl text-gold">18</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-paper/80">Advisory board members</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-6">Who we serve</div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">
            Three rooms. Same standard.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-sans text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">University leaders</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              Presidents, provosts, and deans of continuing education. The pressure is real, the budget
              is finite, the timeline is short. We do not add work for your team. We carry it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="rule-muted" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-sans text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Enterprise leaders</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              Chief learning officers, chief transformation officers, heads of strategy. The workforce
              needs AI fluency now, and the senior team needs a clear read on what is changing in the
              industry. We build both.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="rule-muted" />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-sans text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Senior executives</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              Members and prospective members of the Advisory Board. The Board does serious work that
              informs the institute and the field. If that fits the way you want to spend an hour, we
              should talk.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-paper text-ink border-t border-light-border">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-10">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-on-light mb-3">Recent research</div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">From the institute.</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/insights" class="hidden md:inline-block text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink">
          All insights &rsaquo;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10">
        <a href="/insights/ai-readiness-gap-2026-updated.html" class="block group">
          <article class="border-t-2 border-rule pt-5 h-full">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted mb-3">Report &middot; 2026</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3 group-hover:text-gold-deep transition-colors">AI readiness gap</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              How Fortune 500 organizations are actually adopting AI, and where the gap lives between
              executive intent and operator capability.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 group-hover:text-ink">
              Read the report &rsaquo;
            </span>
          </article>
        </a>
        <a href="/insights/ai-skills-gap-2026.html" class="block group">
          <article class="border-t-2 border-rule pt-5 h-full">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted mb-3">Report &middot; 2026</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3 group-hover:text-gold-deep transition-colors">AI skills gap</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              What the workforce needs to learn next, surfaced from interviews with the people closest to
              the work.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 group-hover:text-ink">
              Read the report &rsaquo;
            </span>
          </article>
        </a>
        <a href="/insights/agent-readiness-gap-2026.html" class="block group">
          <article class="border-t-2 border-rule pt-5 h-full">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-muted mb-3">Report &middot; 2026</div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-3 group-hover:text-gold-deep transition-colors">Agent readiness gap</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-ink/90">
              Why enterprises are deploying AI agents faster than they can govern them. The
              deployment curve is now ahead of the oversight curve.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 group-hover:text-ink">
              Read the report &rsaquo;
            </span>
          </article>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-prose-wide">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-6">Start a conversation</div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-paper">
          The first step is a conversation.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg text-paper/85 max-w-prose-narrow">
          Whether you are a university partner, an enterprise buyer, or a senior operator considering
          the Board, the first step is a short conversation. We will tell you honestly whether there is
          a fit. If there is not, we will say so.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Request a conversation</a>
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Read the research</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
